:::Hot Rod:::

Hot Rod was now reprogramed to evil, to searve the Alliance. His dark
side was awoken. He looked at Feline.
"Thank you." With his dark side awake, he didn't hold back feelings. He
grabbed Feline, rudely. He forced a kiss.
